Hi all,
  I have installed the most recent version of Cantera 1.5.5 for 
Windows XP and am learning and enjoying MixMaster. I get an error 
however when I try to open the 'Reaction Paths...' window, see text 
from the cmd prompt below. When the Reaction Paths window opens it is 
blank, it seems that 'rxnpath.gif' is not recognized.
  Have others had this problem? I saw no similar posts, except 662 
which had a different MixMaster problem. I do not look forward to 
reinstalling everything as all the other functions seem to work (I am 
using the Matlab interface). Thoughts are welcome,
- Carl
